narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Calc BC with more series work- manageable if you try. You will learn fairly interesting stuff for low level math, although the series stuff gets tedious.
This is a good math class.

Boring, bad class. Did all the learning on my own. Struggled to stay awake in class. The tests and problem sets were ok though, I like working on my own and solving math problems. Don't take it with Coifman, take it with one of the TAs.
Math 115 is basically AP Calc BC at a fast pace. Nothing too special. Just weekly problem sets, 2 mid-terms, and a final. Do all your work and you'll be fine.
